{"article_id":"P5Vh5klan8KmZV2M","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump invoked on Sunday past pro-border security comments by two unlikely political adversaries","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"-- Barack Obama and Hillary Clinton --","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"as the ongoing partial federal government shutdown over border wall funding enters its third week .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"In a pair of early-morning posts on Twitter , Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"who later headed to a meeting with advisers at Camp David","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to discuss border security ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"also seemingly addressed reports","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"that the prolonged shutdown will end up costing the government more than the $ 5 billion","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"he has requested for the wall ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"writing","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"that in the end , a `` properly planned and constructed Wall will pay for itself many times a year ! ''","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Trump 's remarks underscored his apparent unwillingnesss to compromise on securing at least some of the border wall funding","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"he has demanded ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"despite the insistence of House Speaker Nancy Pelosi","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"that Democrats will never pay for a wall .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"However , in an interview","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"broadcast Sunday on NBC 's `` Meet the Press , '' Acting White House Chief of Staff Mick Mulvaney told host Chuck Todd","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that Trump `` was willing to agree ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and he mentioned this at the Rose Garden press conference ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to take a concrete wall off the table . ''","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Mulvaney had met with senior congressional officials on Saturday","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"to try to make progress on a compromise ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"although he suggested","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"the encounter had been mostly unproductive .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"IN SITUATION ROOM MEETING , SCHUMER , PELOSI INTERRUPT DHS SECRETARY WITHIN 5 SECONDS","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"`` Again , what 's driving this is the president 's desire","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"to change the conditions at the border , ''","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Mulvaney said .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"`` And","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"if he has to give up a concrete wall ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"replace it with a steel fence","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"in order to do that","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"so that Democrats can say ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"'See ?","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"He 's not building a wall anymore '","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that should help us move in the right direction . ''","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"On Twitter , the president intimated","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"that cynical political considerations were motivating Democrats ' rejection of wall funding .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Pelosi and other Democrats have suggested","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"they would be willing to fund general border security efforts , but not a wall .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"( The president has told Democrats","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"the shutdown could last more than a year . )","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"\" 'We simply can not allow people to pour into the United States undetected , undocumented , unchecked ... ' \" Barrack Obama , 2005 , ''","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"Trump wrote on Sunday ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"quoting the former president in 2005 .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Then-Sen. Obama made the remarks at a press conference with then-Florida GOP Sen. Mel Martinez , as part of a bipartisan effort","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"to address illegal immigration .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Obama 's full quote at the time :","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"`` We simply can not allow people to pour into the United States , undetected , undocumented , unchecked","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and circumventing the line of people","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"who are waiting patiently , diligently and lawfully","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"to become immigrants in this country . ''","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"`` We all agree on the need","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"to better secure the border","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"and to punish employers","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"who choose to hire illegal immigrants , ''","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Obama added .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"`` We are a generous and welcoming people , here in the United States ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"but those","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"who enter the country illegally ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"and those","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"who employ them ,","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"disrespect the rule of law","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"and they are showing disregard for those","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"who are following the law . ''","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"Obama went on to advocate for imposing a `` hefty fine '' on those","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"already in the country illegally , as well as tighter border security measures .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"In his post , Trump also provided a partial quote from former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"emphasizing her support for the Secure Fence Act of 2006 .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"That legislation passed by an overwhelming 80-19 majority ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"and was backed by Obama , as well .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"`` I voted ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"when I was a Senator ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"to build a barrier","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to try to prevent illegal immigrants from coming in ... \" Hillary Clinton , 2015 , ''","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Trump wrote .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"`` We ' re not doing a wall . ''","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"- Speaker of the House Nancy Pelosi","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"At a campaign stop in November 2015 , Clinton told a crowd :","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"`` I voted numerous times","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"when I was a senator","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"to spend money","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"to build a barrier","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"to try to prevent illegal immigrants from coming in .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"And I do think","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"you have to control your borders . ''","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Trump continued :","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"`` The only reason","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"they do not want to build a Wall","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"is that Walls Work !","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"99 % of our illegal Border crossings will end ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"crime in our Country will go way down","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and we will save billions of dollars a year !","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"A properly planned and constructed Wall will pay for itself many times a year ! ''","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Last week , former White House Chief of Staff John Kelly flatly asserted in an interview with The Los Angeles Times","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"that the president 's proposed border project `` is not a wall ''","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"and that all plans for a concrete wall were abandoned long ago","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"-- directly contradicting the White House 's repeated claims .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"In a series of Twitter posts last month , Trump insisted","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"that `` we are not building a Concrete Wall ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"we are building artistically designed steel slats ,","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"so that you can easily see through it . ''","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"But Kelly 's comments were seemingly at odds with the president 's multiple tweets","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"calling for `` money","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"to finish the Wall , ''","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"as well as his promises during and after the 2016 presidential campaign .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"`` To be honest ,","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"it ' s not a wall , \"","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"Kelly said in an interview with The Los Angeles Times .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"\" The president still says ' wall '","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"- oftentimes frankly he ' ll say ' barrier ' or ' fencing , '","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"now he ' s tended toward steel slats .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"But we left a solid concrete wall early on in the administration ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"when we asked people what they needed","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"and where they needed it . ''","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"Pelosi ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"after regaining the speakership this week ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"made clear","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"that no wall of any kind was on the table .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"`` We ' re not doing a wall , ''","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"Pelosi told reporters .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"`` Does anybody have any doubt about that ?","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"We are not doing a wall .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"So that ' s that .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"It has nothing to do with politics .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"It has to do with :","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"The wall is an immorality between countries .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"It ' s an old way","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"of thinking","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"[ and ] it isn ' t cost-effective . \"","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"At one point during a meeting at the White House on Wednesday ,","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"according to the Wall Street Journal ,","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"Pelosi interrupted Homeland Security Secretary Kirstjen Nielsen","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"while she was citing statistics","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"related to the border ,","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"including how many criminal illegal immigrants attempted to enter the U.S. last year .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":271,"left":159,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":138,"right":158,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":138,"left":137,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":145,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":143,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":140,"right":142,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":140,"left":3,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":6,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":148,"right":156,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":146,"right":147,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":152,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":149,"right":151,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":150,"right":19,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"purpose","nucleari